> In a 70 (4 wheel drums) how many wheel cylinders are needed for each FRONT 
> wheel?  Two? Four?
>
> PEACE!
> John Baker

Two cylinders for each front wheel (one cylinder for each rear wheel). 
Check your star adjusters to be sure
they haven't frozen up, so you can adjust your brakes.

